Function object type that provides Point_3 operator()(Origin p) returning the point with 0, 0, 0 as Cartesian coordinates and Point_3 operator()(FT x, FT y, FT z) returning the point with x, y and z as Cartesian coordinates.

Function object type that provides Vector_3 operator()(Point_3 p1, Point_3 p2) and Vector_3 operator()(Origin p1, Point_3 p2) returning the vector p1p2, Vector_3 operator()(NULL_VECTOR) returning the null vector, and Vector_3 operator()(Line_3 l) returning a vector having the same direction as l
Function object type that provides Line_2 operator()(Point_2 p, Vector_2 d) returning the line going through p in the direction of d.
Function object type that provides Point_2 operator()(Line_2 l, int i) returning an arbitrary point on l.

detaileddescription.para: i is not used and can be of any value.

briefdescription.para: Function object type that provides Point_2 operator()(FT x, FT y) returning the 2D point with x and y as Cartesian coordinates.
Function object type that provides Vector_2 operator()(Point_2 p1, Point_2 p2) returning the vector p1p2, Vector_2 operator()(NULL_VECTOR) returning the null vector.
Function object type that provides Tetrahedron_3 operator(Point_3 p, Point_3 q, Point_3 r, Point_3 s) returning the tetrahedron with the points p, q, r and s.
Function object type that provides FT operator()(Point_3 p) and FT operator()(Vector_3 v) returning the x coordinate of a point and a vector respectively.
Function object type that provides FT operator()(Point_3 p) and FT operator()(Vector_3 v) returning the y coordinate of a point and a vector respectively.
Function object type that provides FT operator()(Point_3 p) and FT operator()(Vector_3 v) returning the z coordinate of a point and a vector respectively.
Function object type that provides FT operator()(Point_2 p) and FT operator()(Vector_2 v) returning the x coordinate of a point and a vector respectively.
Function object type that provides FT operator()(Point_2 p) and FT operator()(Vector_2 v) returning the y coordinate of a point and a vector respectively.
Function object type that provides FT operator()(Vector_2 v) returning the squared length of v.
Function object type that provides FT operator()(Vector_3 v1, Vector_3 v2) returning the scalar product of v1 and v2.
Function object type that provides Vector_3 operator() (Vector_3 v1, Vector_3 v2) returning the v1+v2.
Function object type that provides Vector_3 operator()(Plane_3 p) returns a vector that is orthogonal to the plane p and directed to the positive side of p.

Function object type that provides Plane_3 operator()(Point_3 p, Point_3 q, Point_3 r) creates a plane passing through the points p, q and r and Plane_3 operator()(Point_3 p, Vector_3 v) introduces a plane that passes through point p and that is orthogonal to V.
Function object type that provides Vector_3 operator()(Plane_3 h, Point_3 p) returns the orthogonal projection ofpontoh`.
Function object type that provides bool operator()(Point_3 p, Point_3 q, Point_3 r) returning true if the points p, q, and r are collinear and false otherwise.

Function object type that provides Oriented_size operator()(Plane_3 h, Point_3 p) returns CGAL::ON_ORIENTED_BOUNDARY, CGAL::ON_NEGATIVE_SIDE, or CGAL::ON_POSITIVE_SIDE, depending on the position of p relative to the oriented plane h.
A concept that describes the set of types required by the CGAL::Kinetic_space_partition_3.
